},
"children":[
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"aca139",
"children":[
"Treatment can be effective during the early proliferative phase. Testosterone is indicated for confirmed hypogonadism; otherwise, choose selective estrogen receptor modulators and aromatase inhibitors."
]
},
{
"type":"heading",
"class":"tricked",
"children":[
