]
},
{
"type":"list",
"class":"tricked",
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"list-item",
"hlId":"5b5430",
"children":[
"Differentiate gynecomastia from pseudogynecomastia, which is fat deposition typically seen in men with obesity."
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"list-item",
"hlId":"4472b3",
"children":[
"Obtain mammography for unilateral, nontender, or fixed masses to diagnose breast cancer."
